casebody.data:
First Department,

December, 1955

(December 1, 1955) In the Matter of Ministers, Elders & Deacons of the Reformed Protestant Dutch Church of the City of New York, Respondent, against Nathan Donfer et al., Respondents, and Nathan Greenbaum & Co. Inc., Appellant.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, with $10 costs. Concur — Breitel, J. P., Bastow, Botein and Rabin, JJ.
